name: Tua Tempestade
description:
the smoke makes you see the wind
invisible refreshment of my life
windblow
which feeds me on fire 
passes on me
I wait for you so hot
thirsty for this air to breathe... deep

I look up 
the clouds are running in a hurry. 
I arrived
your storm

text @eroticasalome from the book "Travessia de Salomé"
music @wasem_simon
